    "SheetAgent comprises two essential components for agent actions: a Planner and an Informer.",
    "The Planner generates Python code and employs a ReAct-style reasoning approach to manipulate the spreadsheet table.",
    "The Informer serves as an evidence provider, supplying subtask-specific SQL queries to assist the Planner in tackling complex tasks.",
